version_description:
- Various updates to further support iOS 11 and the new iPhone8 and above
- Added a fix for a small subset of users experiencing subscription issues

The app is fully redesigned from top to bottom!

* The all-new design makes it way easier to do everything on Whitepages, including finding people and businesses, identifying unknown callers and spam calls, and looking up addresses.
* We significantly improved performance - the app is faster and more stable, so you get the information you want more quickly and reliably.
* We added even more data on people, businesses, phone numbers and properties, so the most trusted name in people search has even more contact information - including caller ID data and hard to find mobile numbers - than ever before.
* Access people background reports and premium contact information on Whitepages Premium web with your account.
